## Patent Defense

If you make a written claim that the software infringes a
patent, your patent license for the software ends immediately.
If your company makes such a claim, your patent license for
the software ends for work on behalf of that company.

## Violations

If you violate these terms, your licenses from the licensor
end immediately.  However, if you've never been notified of a
violation of these terms by the licensor before, and you come
into full compliance and take practical steps to correct past
violations within 32 days of the notification, your licenses
resume.

